WEBVTT

00:00:00.371 --> 00:00:04.386
So, I guess it is a result
of globalization

00:00:04.410 --> 00:00:08.014
that you can find Coca-Cola tins
on top of Everest

00:00:08.038 --> 00:00:09.976
and a Buddhist monk in Monterey.

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:12.374
(Laughter)

00:00:12.880 --> 00:00:17.975
And so I just came,
two days ago, from the Himalayas

00:00:17.999 --> 00:00:19.419
to your kind invitation.

00:00:19.443 --> 00:00:23.572
So I would like to invite you, also,
for a while, to the Himalayas themselves.

